! Hybrid Abelian Non-Abelian Sandpile

Candidate routing split: Abelian redistribution handles safe, order-insensitive
relaxation, while non-Abelian routing preserves path-sensitive novelty.

!! Role

This gives [[Chirality Destabilizer]] a bounded mechanism instead of turning
novelty into a free-for-all.

